p width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uaiione.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Aiione</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/7/02 8:56:22 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9755.topic>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Va'Dyn</span><hr size=1> Any idea on his spawn time? Or if he's triggered, how do you trigger him?<br><br>He's a large rock like golem in Akheva Ruins. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usouthernkreuz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Southern Kreuz</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/7/02 10:30:12 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9755.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> heyo</span><hr size=1> think it has something to do with the number of mind burrowers killed in a 3 day time span<br><br>southern <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/umemnenthmoondust.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Memnenth Moondust</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/7/02 11:26:27 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9755.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: heyo</span><hr size=1> I think he is a PH mob, when he dies a nother mob will spawn in his spot in the normal cycle time.<br><br>Logic dictates that he is a normal PH mob, but of course since I dont have evidence of killing the PH and forcing a spawn, I cant really say for certain. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/utalanic.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Talanic</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/7/02 1:54:01 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9755.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Hmm.</span><hr size=1> All I can say is my guild's killed him 4-5 times.  Never any word of any PH being there... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uavrus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Avrus</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/7/02 2:39:03 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9755.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hmm.</span><hr size=1> He's always been timed when we killed him Tal.<br><br>We never had to pop him. Don't know the respawn time.<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uvilexx.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Vilexx</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/7/02 2:51:49 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9755.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hmm.</span><hr size=1> Nope he definately has a ph.<br>Little non-rubblerouser guy laying down where VD normally spawns.<br><br>-Vilexx<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/usejineq.showPublicProfile?language=EN>SejinEQ</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/7/02 3:03:18 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9755.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hmm.</span><hr size=1> We've gotten him 7 times and all predictable.  3 day spawn<br><br>Sejin Saotome<br>Grandmaster <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ukarangithzerai.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Karan Githzerai</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/7/02 6:04:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9755.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hmm.</span><hr size=1> He does seem to have a ph, as a rubble rouser stands in his static spot when he is not there.  However, his spawn seems to be very constant.  3 days almost on the dot, maybe +/- an hour or two.  I recall one time I went to check on him when we knew he would be spawning soon, he was not up but the rouser was.  I had him in my target as I was running back to the group and it disappeared.  I thought at first maybe I had targeted a trap or something but I went back to his spot a few minutes later and he was up. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ubartfast.showPublicProfile?language=EN>bartfast</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/25/02 6:16:43 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9755.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Hmm.</span><hr size=1> Hi folks,<br>small problem here, maybe someone can iluminate me.<br><br>Allthough i could hear him casting, i was unable to locate him. He didnt even show up on track. See invis didnt change that either.<br><br>So please some one tell me where is usual spawnpoint actually is. Maybe even with a loc according to this map: <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.circleofsouls.org/maps/luclin/AkhevaRuins.jpg">www.circleofsouls.org/map...aRuins.jpg</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br><br>Thanks in advance<br><br>Zlarti <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uharbogast.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Harbogast</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/25/02 6:32:27 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9755.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Va'Dyn</span><hr size=1> Yeah there is a trap near Va'dynns spawn that has some lame ass message &quot;Va'dyn begins to cast a spell&quot;. I had my guild go to akheva because of it and it turned out he wasnt up. I was pissed. Just get a tracker, hes easily trackable from zone area. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uvedair.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Vedair</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/25/02 6:41:23 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9755.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Va'Dyn</span><hr size=1> another question - our guild killed him a few times now, first time he dropped 2 60 luclin spells, but the other times just crap items(belt, crown and so on). did VI nerf that or is it just random? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uprodigious.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Prodigious</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Safehouse Supporter</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(2/25/02 6:44:51 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9755.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Va'Dyn</span><hr size=1> i think it's random. one time we got 1 lvl 60 spell and some item, other times just one item or two items (and no spells). not a very reliable source for high lvl spells it seems (nor phat lewt) <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showPrevMessage?topicID=9755.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showNextMessage?topicID=9755.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousethebackroomsecretsspoilers.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=9755.topic&index=11><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% b